trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma coleção somente leitura de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> classe representa uma coleção somente leitura de objetos, normalmente usado por <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objetos para gerenciar conjuntos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> controlar usa um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> coleção para manter uma lista de disponíveis <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos em uma página, enquanto um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> objeto usa um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> coleção para controlar o disponíveis <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos que ele contém.

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Embora o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> coleção é somente leitura, você pode fazer alterações programáticas para as propriedades dos controles subjacentes referenciado na coleção.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection.CopyTo%2A> método é útil quando você deseja montar uma matriz personalizada que pode conter todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> coleção, um subconjunto desses objetos, ou um subconjunto desses objetos.
